- Gusoma ibitabo barikumwe n’umwana bakavuga ku mashusho;
- Kubwira umwana udukuru no kumwigisha kuririmba;
- Guha umwana isahani ye yo kuriraho;
- Gukomeza gushishikariza umwana kurya bamuha igihe gihagije;
- Kwigisha umwana kwiyambika imyenda, gukoresha umusarani neza no gukaraba intoki akoresheje amazi mezan’isabuni nyuma yo kwituma na mbere yo kurya;
- Kumva no gusubiza ibibazo byose by’abana;
- Kumushishikariza guhimba udukino tw’abana no gushushanya;
- Guha umwana uturimo duto duto nko gusubiza ibikinisho mu  mwanya wabyo mu rwego rwo kubatoza kugira inshingano;
- Kubuza abana kureba televiziyo mu gihe kitari ngombwa no mu gihe cy’ibiganiro birimo amashusho akanganye;
- Kumushishikariza kugira imyitwarire myizano kumushyiriraho ibyo atagomba kurenga mu rwego rwo kumutoza imico myiza;
- Kumwereka urukundo buri gihe;
- Niba hari ahantu ha ho kwigira imikino y’abana, umwana agomba kujyanwayo mu rwego rwo kumumenyereza gahunda y’ishuri.
